{"tid":1740783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇人踩人？大家快啲入黎 backup!!","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T00:01:13.000Z","uid":152284,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"297a15b2874b0182872fa6a23e0b6f58a5391be5","tid":1740783,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"【11.18 油麻地人踩人事件】<br />\n<br />\n昨晚約11時半，一批示威者被警方追趕到油麻地港鐵站外時，當中有人跘倒地上，引致人踩人及人叠人的險況，現場所見有人被壓或踏在人群底下。當時現場有消防員及義務急救員正在協助救人，有消防員努力拉起部份人士，但當警員趕至時卻阻止所有救援行動，將消防員及急救員與示威者分隔開，並阻止記者上前拍攝。警員最後將救人及提供協助的市民全數拘捕，但並未向倒下受壓的示威者伸出援手。而本媒記者在拍攝現場時，更被警員以胡椒噴霧攻擊，妨礙及阻止記者拍攝採訪。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥於今午記者會表示，未接報昨日在油麻地的驅散行動中出現「人踩人」的情況。警方的說法明顯與事實不乎，事實上昨晚的情況是「人踩人」加上「人叠人」，並最終導致有31名傷者送院治理，當中16人被分類為嚴重個案。到底是前線警員隱瞞事實沒有上報實際情況，或是警方故意向公眾發報虛假資訊，以淡化事件逃避見死不救的責任，均是公眾不能接受的可恥行為。<br />\n<br />\n攝 / Kaiser@ USP United Social Press 社媒<br />\n<br />\n#USP #香港 #hongkong #反送中 #反送中條例遊行 #逃犯條例 #香港加油 #antiextraditionlaw #extraditionlaw #freehongkong #光復香港時代革命 #五大訴求 #五大訴求缺一不可 #USP20191118 #油麻地 #人踩人 #人叠人<br />\n<br />\n【新設】USP Instagram account： <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fuspunitedsocialpress%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=25da6347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/uspunitedsocialpress/</a> USP Telegram Channel： <a href=\"https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUSP_United_Social_Press&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=dcce6e51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/USP_United_Social_Press</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C76FSrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC76FSrp.jpg&h=f7a38a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX0bY6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX0bY6q.jpg&h=e8546e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2Xqi6r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2Xqi6r.jpg&h=bb41b581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfdQvc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfdQvc7.jpg&h=6c2f23b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGZoQc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGZoQc8.jpg&h=202a72fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqjHmjP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqjHmjP.jpg&h=9d3ba661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUCJQdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUCJQdb.jpg&h=31f381f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E24PLMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE24PLMx.jpg&h=4cfe2c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//////////<br />\n大家唔好俾人洗走啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec1c06431a50c460b5bb982985077def71b3c03","tid":1740783,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"睇圖都覺得好撚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882f44e6d96c6a215bcaa21d7f0a258ce00a8749","tid":1740783,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a963fe53b8728c38f419eb3fde7c1e68c5cd0e","tid":1740783,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/